These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
City: prague, marseilles, edinburgh
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, siglo, tiparillo
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, d&b, dubstep
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
3 different games are played: billiard, poker, bridge
 1. the person playing billiard is the german##1
 2. the person playing bridge is the mechanic##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the italian and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the designer is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is the colombian##1
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 8. the person playing poker is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the person playing billiard is on the left of the designer##1
10. the siglo-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| City          | marseilles       | edinburgh    | prague         |
| Cigar         | siglo    | tiparillo  | havana        |
| Job           | accountant | designer   | mechanic      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | dubstep    | country       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Game         | billiard     | poker | bridge |

