.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, sprite
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, singing, gardening
House: cottage, farmhouse, wooden
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, zinnia, aconite
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the person who growsaconite is the british##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the dutch is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the cottage house##1
 7. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the wooden house##1
10. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | sprite    | juice         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | gardening  | singing     |
| House   | wooden       | farmhouse      | cottage         |
| Nationality   | dutch      | british   | australian    |
| Flower           | lily        | aconite      | zinnia         |
| Sport         | water-polo | baseball  | weightlifting |

