.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, kale, peas
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, skydiving
3 different games are played: go, billiard, backgammon
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, august, february
House: gothic-revival, farmhouse, townhouse
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, swimming
 1. the person eating kale is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the townhouse house is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person playing go is the person eating peas##1
 4. the person playing billiard is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the farmhouse house and the person who's birthday is in february##2
 8. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating kale##1
11. the farmhouse house is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Food          | peas      | kale      | cabbage      |
| Hobby         | fishing   | skydiving | magic-tricks |
| Game   | go | billiard    | backgammon          |
| Birthday   | august       | december      | february          |
| House   | farmhouse    | gothic-revival  | townhouse      |
| Pet           | hamster   | hedgehog  | mouse        |
| Sport         | climbing  | sailing   | swimming     |

