The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, jazz, pop
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, zinnia, marigold
3 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, mouse
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who growsmarigold##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 4. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of country##1
 5. the fan of country is between the person eating grapefruit and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the fan of country is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the musician is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the person drinking milk is between the musician and the social-worker##2
10. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | milk           | soy-milk      |
