 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is swimming and the cape-cod house##2
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 7. the person driving the bike is between the person eating strawberry and the person traveling to boston##2
 8. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 9. the journalist is on the right of the craftsman house##1
10. the engineer is the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
