City: boston, san-francisco, nizza
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, soccer, water-polo
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, taxi, van
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who growstulip##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the person drinking almond-milk and the cottage house##2
 8. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person who growstulip is the person driving the subway##1
10. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
11. the person driving the subway is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | tea      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| Flower   | zinnia | orchid  | tulip |
| House   | craftsman  | cape-cod     | cottage |
| City           | boston        | nizza | san-francisco     |
| Sport         | handball    | water-polo | soccer   |
| Transport     | taxi        | van        | subway   |

