.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, funk, classical
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, hiking, singing
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, musician
3 different pets are kept: pony, guinea-pig, frog
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, cain, dannemann
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, skateboard
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the musician##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the fan of classical##1
3. the fan of funk is on the left of the dressmaker##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is between the owner of the pony and the manager##2
5. the fan of classical is between the musician and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the fan of classical##1
7. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | fanta      | juice      | milk       |
| Music-Genre          | funk      | classical    | d&b   |
| Hobby         | singing    | baking     | hiking     |
