The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, scientific, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, reggae
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, december, october
House: modern, ranch-style, farmhouse
1. the ranch-style house is the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
5. the polish is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
6. the egyptian is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
8. the modern house is the person watching superhero movies##1
9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | fanta       | coffee     | cola         |
| Nationality          | dutch     | polish      | egyptian     |
| Hobby         | photography | reading    | cooking      |
