.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, tea
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, spinach, zucchini
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, lilac, brown
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, french, italian
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, rabbit
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, ritmeester, montecristo
3 different games are played: poker, chess, canasta
1. the person drinking milk is the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person playing canasta is the blend-smoker##1
3. the person who likes red is between the person drinking tea and the owner of the rabbit##2
4. the canadian is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
6. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
7. the person who likes lilac is the person eating broccoli##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the french is between the person eating broccoli and the person playing poker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | milk       | tea      |
| Food          | broccoli   | zucchini   | spinach  |
| Color           | lilac  | red | brown    |
| Nationality   | canadian   | french     | italian  |
| Pet           | rabbit     | dog        | hedgehog |
| Cigar         | ritmeester | blend   | montecristo  |
| Game     | chess    | canasta     | poker      |

 